<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/BallAerospace/COSMOS/issues/672">#672</a> Secure COSMOS API with Shared Secret</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/BallAerospace/COSMOS/issues/1227">#1227</a> Prevent a Malicious Website From Sending Commands</li>
</ul>

